    • missing.game.Game
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Game
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class assumes that when the game is initialised, the XMLHandler is passed in a file and the players had picked their avatars.
